RDFpro library.

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Mapper
    Mapper function in a MapReduce job.

    A generic RDF stream transformer.
    RDFSource
    A source of RDF data.
    Reducer
    Reduce function in a MapReduce job.
    Transformer
    A generic Statement -> Statement [0..*] transformer.
